This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with neural machine translation models and language modeling. It could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it proposes a new architecture for the transformer model. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it deals with natural language processing and machine translation. The paper also mentions the use of convolutional neural networks (CNNs) for image captioning, which could place it under cs.CV (Computer Vision). Finally, the paper mentions the use of locality constraints, which could place it under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it deals with neural network architectures.
